Date: Thu, 22 Jan 2026 11:37:40 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 01/18] feat: add Rounded connector mode and reorder shape menu

- Add ConnectorMode.Rounded enum value
- Add cornerRadius property to ConnectorElementModel (default 20px)
- Create ConnectorRIcon for rounded connector button
- Update connector menus (toolbar, dense menu, tool button)
- Reorder shape menu: Rect, RoundedRect, Ellipse, Diamond
- Move Triangle to ExtendedShapeConfig for shape browser

Note: Rounded connector path generation not yet implemented.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
